					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <hr /> <blockquote> <p><span style="color:green">Like this piece? See it and many more saplings like it, at Popsioak's Garden, <a href="http://scp-wiki.net/popsioaks-garden" target="_blank">here!</a></span></p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p><em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sX3uMbROMg8">i, far removed from myself</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sX3uMbROMg8">had denied what I lost when my heart had withdrawn to the fray</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sX3uMbROMg8">in a whimsical way, i would flee from the truth</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sX3uMbROMg8">i could bury in youth</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sX3uMbROMg8">you would have me, if I'd fallen again?</a></strong></em><br /> <em><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sX3uMbROMg8">would you bring me back out of the dark, with my lungs of a lark?</a></strong></em></p> <p><strong><em>cold have i calloused but these walls are coming down.</em></strong></p> </blockquote> </div> <hr /> <blockquote> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anorrack" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4188420&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591758098" alt="Anorrack" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4188420)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/anorrack" >Anorrack</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591758098" alt="Veralta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" >Veralta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brewsterion-1017" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3093017&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591758098" alt="Brewsterion 1017" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3093017)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/brewsterion-1017" >Brewsterion 1017</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4646198&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591758098" alt="BlueJones" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4646198)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bluejones" >BlueJones</a></span> and Justice.<br /> Also thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591758098" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span> for my first use of the lovely Flopstyle CSS!</p> </blockquote> <p>Giving it a shot. here we go.</p> <p>Spoilers.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Currant made a lil' neighborhood. How sweet.</p> </div> </div> </div> <br /> image creds below :) <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Underwater_mcmurdo_sound.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Underwater_mcmurdo_sound.jpg</a> - PD<br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:AT_THE_RESEARCH_STATION_ON_POLLUTION_AND_SUPERSATURATION_OF_THE_NATIONAL_ENVIRONMENTAL_RESEARCH_CENTER,_A_MARINE..._-_NARA_-_545206.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:AT_THE_RESEARCH_STATION_ON_POLLUTION_AND_SUPERSATURATION_OF_THE_NATIONAL_ENVIRONMENTAL_RESEARCH_CENTER,_A_MARINE..._-_NARA_-_545206.jpg</a> - PD<br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:The_underwater_surface_structures_of_an_iceberg_in_Svalbard.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:The_underwater_surface_structures_of_an_iceberg_in_Svalbard.jpg</a> cc-by-sa-4.0<br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Krill_on_finger.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Krill_on_finger.jpg</a> - PD<br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Unusual_type_of_deep_sea_medusae.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Unusual_type_of_deep_sea_medusae.jpg</a> - PD<br /> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Deep_sea_corals,_Wagner_Seamount.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Deep_sea_corals,_Wagner_Seamount.jpg</a> - PD</p> </div> </div> </div> 
